<div class="text-center main-banner">
  <div class="overlay"></div>

  <div class="content">
    <h1 class="banner-title">Study Share</h1>
    <p>みんなで頑張ろう！！</p>

    <a href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-3">Let's study</a>
    <p class="mt-2">お試しの方はこちらから</p>
    
    <div class="d-grid gap-2 mt-1"> 
      <%= button_to 'ゲストログイン(閲覧用)', users_guest_sign_in_path, method: :post, class: "btn btn-secondary btn-lg" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="container-fluid py-5 text-center section-info">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h5>勉強の記録をつけたい人！</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h5>モチベーションを維持したい人！</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h5>勉強仲間が欲しい人！</h5>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .main-banner {
    height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    background-image: url('<%= asset_path("PK-sc01-PAR55031-j_TP_V4.jpg") %>');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    color: white;
  }

  .banner-title {
    font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .section-info h5 {
    color: #ffffff;
    background-color: #343a40;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background-color: #007bff;
    border: none;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: #0056b3;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background-color: #6c757d;
    border: none;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background-color: #5a6268;
  }
